definitions.definition: Containing less fat, salt, sugar, or calories than normal, or claimed to have such.

examples: You folks reduce it to the bible only as being authoritative, impoverishing the faith. "Christianity Lite", diet Christianity for those who can't handle the Whole Meal.

main_definition: ( of a food or beverage ) Containing less fat, salt, sugar, or calories than normal, or claimed to have such.
secondary_definitions: ( informal , figurative ) Having certain traits subtracted.
